Judul: Most-energetic cosmic rays originate outside Milky Way: Giant observatory in Argentina finally confirms long-suspected theory.
Abstrak:
The Pierre Auger Observatory in Argentina finally has solid evidence that the most energetic particles in
nature come from sources outside the Milky Way. Scientists have suspected this for decades, but weren’t able to confirm it — until now.
Fakultas: Fakultas Matematika dan Ilmu Pengetahuan Alam
